<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../libs/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/checkhistorycost.css">
    <title>历史价格查询</title>
</head>

<body>
    <!--历史价格查询-->
    <div class="seach-history">
        <a href="javascript:;" class="glyphicon glyphicon-menu-left"></a>
        <h1>历史价格查询</h1>
    </div>

    <!--商品链接-->
    <div class="item_link">
        <p>商品链接</p>
        <input class="col-xs-12" type="text" placeholder="请通过购物App中使用分享或浏览器打开商品页面获取商品链接">
    </div>

    <!--按钮-->
    <div class="stap">
        <button class="seach-history-Price">查询历史价格</button>
        <button class="reset">重置</button>
    </div>

    <!--操作说明-->
    <div class="operation">
        <h5>两步操作即可识别商品真假促销</h5>
        <p>1.打开购物APP（如手机淘宝）复制商品链接</p>
        <p>2.打开慢慢买APP，系统自动识别查历史价</p>
    </div>

    <!--中间空白-->
    <div class="meddle"></div>

    <!--底部-->
    <div class="footer">
        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove-sign"></i>
        <div class="media">
            <div class="media-left media-middle">
                <span class="media-object">慢</span>
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h4 class="media-heading">慢慢买</h4>
                    <p>全网比价，历史价格查询</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="javascript:;">立即打开</a>
        </div>
</body>
<script type="text/template" id="inp_tpl">
        %
        <input class="col-xs-12" type="text" placeholder="请通过购物App中使用分享或浏览器打开商品页面获取商品链接">
</script>
<script src="../libs/jquery/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="../libs/bootstrap/js">
</script>
<script src="../js/common/checkhistorycost.js"></script>
</html>